CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 26, 1961, pg. A13 reads: "Leaving Church - Mr. and Mrs. William Henry Lewis smile for the photographer as they leave St. Richard Roman Catholic Church, following their recent wedding. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of wedding party, left to right: Lewis Coles, groom William Henry Lewis, bride Sheldon Juanita DeLaney Lewis wearing knee length lace gown and mantilla, and Patricia Redmond, also including Claude DeLaney and Daniel Delaney, standing in front of Gothic altar, in St. Richard Roman Catholic Church, another version
